The Premiere Athletes, featuring Ari Daivari, Josh Woods, and Tony Nese, faced Adam Priest, Rhett Titus, and Tony Deppen in a dynamic display of teamwork and athleticism.  Beast Mortos clashed with Blake Christian in a singles match that combined high-impact moves with technical prowess.  - Cole Karter and Griff Garrison battled the Spanish Announce Project's Ang√©lico and Serpentico, showcasing high-flying maneuvers and strategic teamwork.
